{"tid":2121314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鯉魚門公園度假村明起接收病情穩定確診者","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T08:43:41.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee45fc73d034fa608a14554768cd2687121d656","tid":2121314,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:34:13.000Z","msg":"鯉魚門公園度假村明起接收病情穩定確診者<br />\n2020-07-23 HKT 11:30<br />\n<br />\n&quot;天水圍醫院副行政總監李立業說，用作社區隔離設施的鯉魚門公園度假村明天開始收症，入院的病人會是50歲以下，有獨立自理能力、病情穩定、已退燒，以及不用食抗病毒藥，醫護人員會每日為病人做深喉唾液測試，兩個樣本呈陰性便可以出院。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539406-20200723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539406-20200723.htm&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=becce9e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539406-20200723.htm&h=93964750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539406-20200723.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">有助舒緩隔離病房壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"35e6fdff43e66330b52bbce83624038bb5d98d92","tid":2121314,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"有無得1000mb上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96beedc9adc5ffb0194c743bfe9d5357e97cb2de","tid":2121314,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"港版火神山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ce70f6bf8ae0f3921fc0ad7d9c07a5fbf523ad","tid":2121314,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96beedc9adc5ffb0194c743bfe9d5357e97cb2de","tid":2121314,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"